{"tid":380041,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"異地戀&姐弟戀 敵不過2年嘅洗禮","createTime":"2017-08-29T20:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T02:28:04.000Z","uid":89882,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4db695c479aa1a12a8b2105a162853714b87f4","tid":380041,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:58:54.000Z","msg":"分左手差唔多1個幾月 <br />\n小弟今年22、我同佢年齡差距4年多 <br />\n前度雖然係大陸嘅女仔、但大家相處模式都無咩問題 <br />\n雖然我地嘅見面時間唔係話好多、多數都要我番去廣州搵佢、但呢2年真係好開心<br />\n多得佢先令我走出好多人生嘅低谷、亦因為佢我自己改變左好多 <br />\n直到上個月 一個好普通嘅夜晚 佢提出分手 理由係一黎佢屋企摧佢快d結婚、二黎我今年先讀緊year3、工作又未真正穩定。加上我又無能力承諾我一grad就可以搵到份穩定嘅工作等等。我亦好明白一個男仔22歲要一個26歲嘅女朋友等自己、真係好自私。<br />\n我當時雖然不捨、但都好大方接受佢嘅建議、我寧願佢同我提出分手都好過呢句說話由我口中所講出黎、會更傷害到佢。<br />\n宜家我地仲會keep住whatsapp、但呢兩個星期我個心越黎越唔舒服、但我知道無咩機會復合.....唉 <br />\n<br />\n想問下大家點睇異地戀同姐弟戀"},{"pid":"884c74730c5200a0e2864f1601758f53885302be","tid":380041,"uid":52477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:00:30.000Z","msg":"識溝一定係溝姐姐"},{"pid":"107934641bd5cceec0b88cdfacd8359eb65cc983","tid":380041,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:04:18.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始咗段異地戀&amp;姊弟戀關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇見你咁覺得好sad<br />\n利申同ex都係一樣situation"},{"pid":"25e7b7d0a7900a2b1b4cdb42b56ddd4dc7b0127d","tid":380041,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/050717_e2c150681ef1d4bc6b1480ac839789af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F050717_e2c150681ef1d4bc6b1480ac839789af.jpg&h=f5b8190c&s={SIZE}\" />唔知點解會出個咁既廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f6af4b034cdca87a07b8b26102ab5284776f1f","tid":380041,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/050717_e2c150681ef1d4bc6b1480ac839789af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F050717_e2c150681ef1d4bc6b1480ac839789af.jpg&h=f5b8190c&s={SIZE}\" />唔知點解會出個咁既廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我初戀情人就係我老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔關我事"},{"pid":"46e9a5f5a388919b4b86c5ae0d6e22298161ecae","tid":380041,"uid":1675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:21:23.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dfecae1e8cffd983d0ec97f8c0fd068bfc9d83","tid":380041,"uid":16563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:40:06.000Z","msg":"其實見得小  已經無嫁啦<br />\n就算佢話屋企人催婚<br />\n問題係   唔係成日見 都一定遲早散<br />\n見得太多例子<br />\n<br />\n人地工作環境  一定好多狗公埋身<br />\n日日見   就算無狗公<br />\n都好易日耐生情"},{"pid":"f47475725942537e431d6d601a472686963b836a","tid":380041,"uid":82572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:20:41.000Z","msg":"都26歲冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸興早婚<br />\n再加上如果佢願意等你，你要到幾歲先同到佢結婚"},{"pid":"3effa3c981f5b705176b70881607334ccb4e2ae4","tid":380041,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都26歲冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸興早婚<br />\n再加上如果佢願意等你，你要到幾歲先同到佢結婚</blockquote><br />\n支那人26 一般仔都生埋"},{"pid":"6cf253ad6ebf9921b35230b241c394ed93067538","tid":380041,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:01:13.000Z","msg":"係咪叫雞沉左船"},{"pid":"74cabf8855698957d4f19b81c5e0628dcadcdb9d","tid":380041,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪叫雞沉左船</blockquote><br />\n擺到明"},{"pid":"a7a7237355a1706a7d1012fcf061e4f789f0a69f","tid":3